OL,7,FAlmost #35 million has been paid out
OL,8,Fto those who suffered a significant
OL,9,Finjury as a result of violence in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland's troubled past.
OL,12,FAn information campaign has been
OL,13,Flaunched to attempt to reach potential
OL,14,Fapplicants living outside of Northern
OL,15,FIreland.
