OL,5,Csought
OL,7,FThe Victims' Payments Board, which is
OL,8,Fresponsible for the Troubles Permanent
OL,9,FDisablement Payment Scheme, said
OL,10,Fanyone who may have suffered permanent
OL,11,Fdisabling physical or psychological
OL,12,Finjuries as a result of a Troubles-
OL,13,Frelated incident should consider
OL,14,Fapplying to the scheme.
OL,16,FLeaflets with further information
OL,17,Fabout the scheme will be delivered to
OL,18,Fevery household in Northern Ireland
OL,19,Ffrom Monday.
