OL,7,FThe leaflet provides information on
OL,8,Fthe key elements of the scheme,
OL,9,Fincluding background information, how
OL,10,Fto make an application, information
OL,11,Faround providing evidence, as well as
OL,12,Fsignposting potential applicants
OL,13,Ftowards the various groups who provide
OL,14,Ffree support services to those wishing
OL,15,Fto apply.
OL,17,FThe scheme opened for applications on
OL,18,FAugust 31, 2021 and the current
OL,19,Fclosing date is August 31, 2026.
