OL,7,FTo date, more than 6,500 applications
OL,8,Fhave been received and more than #34.8
OL,9,Fmillion has been paid out to victims.
OL,11,FThe Victims' Payments Board is
OL,12,Fcommitted to raising awareness about
OL,13,Fthe scheme to ensure everyone who may
OL,14,Fbe eligible to apply can do so.
OL,16,FIt is therefore encouraging anyone
OL,17,Ffrom Great Britain, the Republic of
OL,18,FIreland, Europe and further afield who
OL,19,Fmay have suffered a permanent physical
OL,20,Fand/or psychological disablement to
OL,21,Fconsider applying.
