OL,7,FMore than 500 applications have
OL,8,Falready been received from outside
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,FPaul Bullick, secretary to the board,
OL,12,Fsaid as years pass it is becoming more
OL,13,Furgent that those injured in the
OL,14,FTroubles should make an application to
OL,15,Fthe scheme.
