OL,7,F"We are all aware of the many Troubles-
OL,8,FRelated incidents which have taken
OL,9,Fplace across Great Britain, Ireland
OL,10,Fand wider Europe over the past five
OL,11,Fdecades where many people received
OL,12,Fdisabling injuries," he said.
OL,14,F"As the years roll on, it is becoming
OL,15,Fmore urgent that those injured in
OL,16,Fthese Troubles-related incidents
OL,17,Fshould make themselves known to us.
