OL,7,F"To this end the Victims' Payments
OL,8,FBoard isreaching out to every
OL,9,Fhousehold in Northern Ireland with
OL,10,Fdetailed information about the scheme
OL,11,Fand we would ask everyone to read this
OL,12,Fcarefully and, if you know of someone
OL,13,Fwho may be eligible to make an
OL,14,Fapplication, to please pass this on.
OL,16,F"We are receiving a large volume of
OL,17,Fapplications, and it is important to
OL,18,Fstress that the decision process could
OL,19,Fbe a lengthy one.
