OL,7,F"These are complex matters, and no two
OL,8,Fapplications are the same. Each one
OL,9,Fmust be considered on its own merit
OL,10,Fand while we have taken steps to
OL,11,Fensure that all applications are
OL,12,Fprogressed in a victim-centric way, we
OL,13,Fwould again ask for the public's
OL,14,Fpatience as we carry out the necessary
OL,15,Fchecks."
